           <h2>Fennel</h2>
           <div class="xyz">
               <div class="pqr">
                Fennel, a plant with a pale bulb and long green stalks, is used to add flavor to food.<br>

Its fiber content helps prevent constipation and improves regularity in your digestive tract .<br>

Fennel also contains an antispasmodic agent that relaxes the smooth muscles in your digestive tract. This action can reduce negative digestive symptoms like bloating, flatulence, and cramping .<br>
               
               
