           <h2>Chia seeds</h2>
           <div class="xyz">
               <div class="pqr">
                Chia seeds are an excellent source of fiber, which causes them to form a gelatin-like substance in your stomach, once consumed. They work like a prebiotic, supporting the growth of healthy bacteria in your gut and therein contributing to healthy digestion .<br>

Their fiber content also helps promote bowel regularity and healthy stools.
          
               
              
